00:04.880 --> 00:08.640
and it's also time to apply those measures to our project file,

00:08.900 --> 00:11.030
let's see how this works.

00:11.030 --> 00:18.130
So here I am back in our course project and I am in the data view and in the FACT-Population table.

00:18.530 --> 00:24.100
Now we want to add measures and I think the best way is if we just start, right?

00:24.170 --> 00:30.440
So let's do this by going to the modeling ribbon and now we don't select new column like we did it

00:30.440 --> 00:34.430
before but now we select new measure, like this.

00:34.790 --> 00:43.290
Let's press that and let's name that measure total population because that's what it's going to calculate,

00:43.310 --> 00:49.950
it will just give us out the total amount of all the population that we have in our dataset. To do this,

00:49.970 --> 00:54.920
we simply write sum like this and press tab

00:55.580 --> 01:01.340
and as you can see here, we can now refer to different tables with that measure but we only want to have

01:01.340 --> 01:04.480
the measure of the FACT-Population population table,

01:04.580 --> 01:11.230
so right here. Now if I double-click that and press enter, then you can see nothing, right?

01:11.290 --> 01:13.730
So there wasn't any column added

01:14.020 --> 01:20.680
and this is also a difference to the calculated columns that we had before, as a measure is only a single

01:20.680 --> 01:21.340
value,

01:21.550 --> 01:26.960
you cannot see it in the actual data model, at least not in that area,

01:27.100 --> 01:34.540
you can only see it when we use it in a visualization and it's also only calculated when you use it

01:34.840 --> 01:40.620
which makes it less memory consuming when comparing it to a calculated column

01:40.900 --> 01:45.050
but of course, you can see it right there, in that fields column.

01:45.150 --> 01:47.760
Here we have the total population measure, 

01:47.760 --> 01:53.050
now let's go to report view and see how we can apply such a measure. To do this,

01:53.080 --> 01:59.220
we simply select a report view right here and here we still have our great population chart.

01:59.650 --> 02:01.100
